了 38% 拉美裔注册选民的支持，高于 2020 年同期的 32%。哈里斯的拉美裔注册选民支持率则为 50%。 美国《福布斯》杂志网站称，10 月 31 日的最新调查结果显示，哈里斯目前以 49% 对 48% 的支持率领先特朗普，但支持率仍有变化空间。美媒：特朗普与哈里斯继续决战摇摆州 _ 新闻频道 _ 央视网 (cctv.com)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-24d785f11c8d13240911c52a1d307599_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2901391027"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyPP5ocDPnJtIEAMaCTExMTU1Njg2NyCq1Ze5BjAAOHtAC3IKMjkwMTM5MTAyN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1730624901.58339", "card_id": "Q_477751835", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "黄鳝平时钻进水稻田的泥土里，草也不吃，它们是吃什么长大的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-976c80ee0e03c5eb338054e597063129_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/477751835"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyPP5ocDPnJtIEAMaCDY4NDQ3ODY1IKS8s4gGMAA4rgFADHIJNDc3NzUxODM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1730624901.58553", "card_id": "Q_2121086623", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "今年安卓发生了啥，电池怎么质的飞跃了?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "往年 6.3 尺寸也就 4600 的电池，突然变成 5500+，提升 20% 多，太夸张了，这电池技能怎么突然这么牛。另一方面，只有苹果今年电池几乎没变化，今年 iPhone 销量估计很难看。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-33f8087ef94809d6ccba3b92a4461bf4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", 